{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTP Live Streaming (HLS) reliably delivers media content across a variety of network and bandwidth conditions. However, there are many factors that can impact stream delivery, such as server or encoder failures, caching issues, or network dropouts. Learn the best-practice behaviors that your servers should adopt to maximize reliability, and gain a practical understanding of the errors your app may encounter and how to handle them."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-Sessions","text":"Related Sessions"},{"type":"links","style":"list","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-502-Measuring-and-Optimizing-HLS-Performance","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-504-Advances-in-HTTP-Live-Streaming","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-515-HLS-Authoring-Update"]}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC17","role":"sampleCode","title":"Error Handling Best Practices for HTTP Live Streaming"},"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-514-error-handling-best-practices-for-http-live-streaming"]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Watch Video (18 min)","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2017\/514","isActive":true}},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-514-Error-Handling-Best-Practices-for-HTTP-Live-Streaming"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"WWDC17-Icon.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-Icon.png"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-515-HLS-Authoring-Update":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-515-hls-authoring-update","type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","abstract":[{"text":"HTTP Live Streaming (HLS) reliably delivers video to audiences around the world. Key to this reliability is a comprehensive set of tools to help you author, deliver, and validate the HLS streams you create. See what’s new in these tools, learn the latest authoring recommendations, and how they apply to advances in HLS such as support for HEVC and IMSC1.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-515-HLS-Authoring-Update","title":"HLS Authoring Update"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-504-Advances-in-HTTP-Live-Streaming":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-504-advances-in-http-live-streaming","title":"Advances in HTTP Live Streaming","role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-504-Advances-in-HTTP-Live-Streaming","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTP Live Streaming allows you to stream live and on-demand content to global audiences. Learn about great new features and enhancements to HTTP Live Streaming. Highlights include support for HEVC, playlist metavariables, IMSC1 subtitles, and synchronized playback of multiple streams. Discover how to simplify your FairPlay key handling with the new AVContentKeySession API, and take advantage of enhancements to offline HLS playback."}],"type":"topic","kind":"article"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"title":"Learn More…","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn More…"}],"type":"link","url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2017/514":{"type":"download","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2017\/514","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2017\/514"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC18-502-Measuring-and-Optimizing-HLS-Performance":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTP Live Streaming (HLS) is used to stream live and on-demand content to global audiences. Discover how to adjust and tune stream authoring and delivery elements to improve the viewing experience. Learn how to accurately measure your streaming performance, identify optimization opportunities, and implement changes to your HLS streams that can significantly improve the user experience."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-502-Measuring-and-Optimizing-HLS-Performance","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18-502-measuring-and-optimizing-hls-performance","kind":"article","role":"sampleCode","title":"Measuring and Optimizing HLS Performance"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"abstract":[{"text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","kind":"symbol","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}],"role":"collection","title":"WWDC Notes"},"WWDC17.jpeg":{"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17.jpeg"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17":{"abstract":[{"text":"Xcode 9, Swift 4.0, iOS 11, macOS 10.13 (High Sierra), tvOS 11, watchOS 4.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"New APIs: ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Core NFC"},{"text":" and more.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17","kind":"article","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg"}],"role":"collectionGroup","title":"WWDC17"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}],"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}}}